    "The complexity of this variation requires decomposition and finding similar instances.",
    "Based on individual SHAP values, we were able to identify clusters in which the variables contributed to the prediction of the members in a similar way.",
    "Since in the present work we were interested in the background factors of quits, we searched for background factors among the 70 main quitters.",
    "We divided the quitters into 6 consistent groups based on the Silhouette method detailed in the Methods section.",
    "In this section, we characterize the clusters and present typical termination factors."
